   <div class="frame"> 
    <div class="bit-60 home-p"> 
     <p>At Westmont, we pursue significance. We yearn for something bigger than ourselves, beyond what the world considers success.</p> 
     <p>Rooted in the conviction that Jesus Christ holds first place, we explore our God-given passions, gifts and opportunities. We seek many things, such as vocation, excellence, community, justice, a calling.</p> 
     <p>This adventure lasts a lifetime. Westmont will help you discover your abilities in the classroom and the potential of your walk with God. Learn how to truly make an impact in the world. </p> 
     <p class="join-us">Join us in this pursuit.</p> 
    </div> 
    <div class="bit-40"> 
     <p class="center mag-cover"> <a href="pursuit-mag.html"><img src="images/pursuit-cover.jpg" alt="current pursuit issue" class="mag-cover-size"></a> <br> <a href="pursuit-mag.html">View the Pursuit magazine</a> </p> 
