    <div class="bit-60"> 
     <a id="academics"></a>
     <h2>Study with faculty focused <br>on undergraduates</h2> 
     <p>Your professors will know your name and invite you to meals in their home—nearly half the faculty live next to campus. Engaging teachers and expert scholars, they bring a sense of joy and adventure to the classroom.</p> 
    </div> 
    <div class="bit-5"> 
