   <div class="frame home-section-four"> 
    <a id="residential"></a>
    <div class="bit-2 stat-left"> 
     <h2>Join a residential community of diverse students</h2> 
     <p>When 1,200 students live, learn and worship together, they develop a special bond and build life-long relationships. Our world-class campus life program supports your studies and gives you a chance to live out your faith and learning.</p> 
     <p><img src="images/80percent.png" alt="80 percent" height="100px" class="percent"> <span class="percent-number">80%</span> <br>of students live on campus, creating a vibrant residential community</p> 
    </div> 
    <div class="bit-2 stat-right"> 
     <h2>Christ Holds First Place</h2> 
     <p>Discover what it means when Christ holds first place in your life. Classes with Christian professors and a rich campus ministries program help you learn to love Christ with all your heart and all your mind.</p> 
     <p class="percent-extra-margin"><img src="images/85percent.png" alt="85 percent" height="100px" class="percent"><span class="percent-number"> 85% </span><br>of students participate in volunteer service or outreach before graduating</p> 
    </div> 
