    <div class="bit-60"> 
     <h2>Pursue a life of significance</h2> 
     <p><strong>Westmont helps you prepare for a certain path in an uncertain future.</strong> Not only will you build a life of significance, but you’ll find meaningful work where you can use your gifts and talents. Our alumni have chosen a wide variety of careers throughout the world, seeking to serve God as well as becoming leaders in their professions. However you choose to put your Westmont degree to work, you’ll find that it leads you down thrilling new paths, serving you well as you strive to live the life God has called you to lead.</p> 
    </div> 
